OL,6,F"It's a flat rate whether I use it or
OL,7,Fnot - whether I'm home or not. You
OL,8,Fhave to pay and everyone is stuck with
OL,9,Fthis bill"
OL,11,FThe government is backing heat systems
OL,12,Fthat serve multiple homes as a low
OL,13,Fcarbon option.
OL,15,FIt's been estimated that 900,000
OL,16,Fhouseholds are connected to these
OL,17,Fnetworks, but government figures
OL,18,Fsuggest some have seen bill rises up
OL,19,Fto 450%.
