OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FStephen Knight leads the Heat Network,
OL,12,Fwhich campaigns on behalf of
OL,13,Fcustomers. Although he welcomes the
OL,14,Fnew regulations, he says they don't go
OL,15,Ffar enough.
OL,17,F"These networks are reliant on really
OL,18,Fvolatile and varied commercial energy
OL,19,Fcosts," he told ITV News. "The
OL,20,Fgovernment needs to do more to develop
OL,21,Fthe equivalent to the price cap."
